Fourth Department,

February, 1979

(February 16, 1979) First Trust & Deposit Company, Respondent, v Reynolds Motors, Inc., Appellant.

— Appeal dismissed, without costs, upon stipulation. (Appeal from order of Onondaga County Court — vacate default judgment.) Present— Moule, J. P., Dillon, Hancock, Jr., Schnepp and Witmer, JJ.
